@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.76) + (tmp + 0.19 + tmp + 0.93)) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.60) / (tmp + 0.26 + tmp + 0.56)))
    v1 = (0.75 / wp.exp(v0))
    v2 = (tmp / wp.abs((v1 + 0.41 - tmp + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
